<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.asianpacificpost.com/portal2/402881910674ebab010674f5ad151f17.do.html" class="external text" title="http://www.asianpacificpost.com/portal2/402881910674ebab010674f5ad151f17.do.html" rel="nofollow">Asia's street kids - a looming crisis</a>, The Asian Pacific Post</li>
